{
  "video_id": "YMtsodcAsVU",
  "title": "The Case for Ai Weiwei | The Art Assignment | PBS Digital Studios",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 499.0,
      "end_time": 2660.0,
      "text": "NARRATOR: In 1995,\nChinese artist Ai Weiwei"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2660.0,
      "end_time": 5540.0,
      "text": "photographed himself as he\npicked up a 2000-year-old urn"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5540.0,
      "end_time": 7070.0,
      "text": "and let it smash to the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7070.0,
      "end_time": 9740.0,
      "text": "If we're appalled when\ncultural heritage is destroyed"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9740.0,
      "end_time": 12020.0,
      "text": "in the name of god\nand state, how can we"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12020.0,
      "end_time": 13920.0,
      "text": "possibly defend Ai's action?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 13920.0,
      "end_time": 16670.0,
      "text": "How can we buy a ticket to\nsee photos of it in a museum?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 16670.0,
      "end_time": 19310.0,
      "text": "How can those photos sell\nfor over a million dollars?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 19310.0,
      "end_time": 21740.0,
      "text": "How can this man be one of\nthe most renowned artists"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 21740.0,
      "end_time": 22490.0,
      "text": "of our time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 22490.0,
      "end_time": 25250.0,
      "text": "This is the case for Ai Weiwei."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 25250.0,
      "end_time": 27860.0,
      "text": "Ai Weiwei was born\nin Beijing in 1957"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 27860.0,
      "end_time": 30470.0,
      "text": "to writer Gao Ying and\nfamed poet Ai Qing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 30470.0,
      "end_time": 33140.0,
      "text": "whom communist leader Mao\nZedong initially embraced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 33140.0,
      "end_time": 35480.0,
      "text": "but soon after denounced\nduring the Anti-Rightist"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 35480.0,
      "end_time": 36980.0,
      "text": "Movement of 1958."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 36980.0,
      "end_time": 40070.0,
      "text": "The family was exiled to labor\ncamps in remote provinces"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 40070.0,
      "end_time": 43310.0,
      "text": "until the end of the\nCultural Revolution in 1976."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 43310.0,
      "end_time": 44630.0,
      "text": "They then returned to Beijing."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 44630.0,
      "end_time": 47450.0,
      "text": "And Ai-- and by that, I\nmean AI Weiwei-- enrolled"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 47450.0,
      "end_time": 50570.0,
      "text": "in Beijing Film Academy\nin 1978 and co-founded"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 50570.0,
      "end_time": 52850.0,
      "text": "a group of avant garde\nartists called The Stars."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 52850.0,
      "end_time": 55490.0,
      "text": "In 1981, he decamped\nto the US and settled"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 55490.0,
      "end_time": 57710.0,
      "text": "in New York, where he\nscraped by, hung out"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 57710.0,
      "end_time": 60410.0,
      "text": "with his neighbor, renowned\nbeat poet Allen Ginsberg,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 60410.0,
      "end_time": 63230.0,
      "text": "and took lots and\nlots of pictures."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 63230.0,
      "end_time": 66440.0,
      "text": "He also immersed himself in\nart, studying Marcel Duchamp"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 66440.0,
      "end_time": 69620.0,
      "text": "and considering the idea of\nreadymade as a way to make art."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 69620.0,
      "end_time": 72050.0,
      "text": "When he returned\nto China in 1993,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 72050.0,
      "end_time": 74840.0,
      "text": "he met with a country\nundergoing tremendous change."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 74840.0,
      "end_time": 78290.0,
      "text": "Many were still reeling from the\n1989 Tienanmen Square crackdown"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 78290.0,
      "end_time": 80120.0,
      "text": "on pro-democracy demonstrators."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 80120.0,
      "end_time": 82850.0,
      "text": "And Deng Xiaoping's focus\non economic development"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 82850.0,
      "end_time": 84860.0,
      "text": "had tripped off the\nmassive transformation"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 84860.0,
      "end_time": 86030.0,
      "text": "of China's cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 86030.0,
      "end_time": 88850.0,
      "text": "Ai's urn dropping occurred\nnot long after his return."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 88850.0,
      "end_time": 90980.0,
      "text": "But his irreverence had\nsurfaced before that."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 90980.0,
      "end_time": 93920.0,
      "text": "He turned a critical eye\ntoward all edifices of power"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 93920.0,
      "end_time": 95780.0,
      "text": "at home, as well as abroad."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 95780.0,
      "end_time": 99410.0,
      "text": "Well-versed in antiques, he knew\nthe value of historic objects"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 99410.0,
      "end_time": 101630.0,
      "text": "and the symbolic power\nof manipulating them."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 101630.0,
      "end_time": 104240.0,
      "text": "Chinese antiquities\nbecame Ai's raw material"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 104240.0,
      "end_time": 107390.0,
      "text": "for a new kind of readymade,\ndynamically synthesizing"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 107390.0,
      "end_time": 109490.0,
      "text": "the clash between\nreverence for the past"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 109490.0,
      "end_time": 111590.0,
      "text": "and the irrepressible\ndrive toward the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 111590.0,
      "end_time": 113450.0,
      "text": "for modernization\nis a mixed bag."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 113450.0,
      "end_time": 114980.0,
      "text": "With change, there is loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 114980.0,
      "end_time": 116210.0,
      "text": "History is erased."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 116210.0,
      "end_time": 119420.0,
      "text": "How can we condemn an artist\nfor destroying cultural heritage"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 119420.0,
      "end_time": 122570.0,
      "text": "when his government has raised\nneighborhoods and entire cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 122570.0,
      "end_time": 125600.0,
      "text": "to build new roads,\nbuildings, giant dams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 125600.0,
      "end_time": 126920.0,
      "text": "and Olympic stadiums?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 126920.0,
      "end_time": 129530.0,
      "text": "Ai's work allows us to\nreckon with the destruction"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 129530.0,
      "end_time": 131630.0,
      "text": "that construction requires."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 131630.0,
      "end_time": 134430.0,
      "text": "But to be clear, he is more\nof a creator than destroyer."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 134430.0,
      "end_time": 136640.0,
      "text": "He has repurposed wood\nfrom demolished temples"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 136640.0,
      "end_time": 138920.0,
      "text": "and transformed it into\nintricate and dramatic"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 138920.0,
      "end_time": 139910.0,
      "text": "installations."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 139910.0,
      "end_time": 143750.0,
      "text": "He takes a basic unit-- say, an\nantique stool-- and multiplies"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 143750.0,
      "end_time": 146510.0,
      "text": "it, compounds it, to\nsee where it takes us."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 146510.0,
      "end_time": 149300.0,
      "text": "History that would otherwise\nbe relegated to dusty shops"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 149300.0,
      "end_time": 152720.0,
      "text": "or landfills is made strikingly,\nunforgettably visible."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 152720.0,
      "end_time": 155330.0,
      "text": "And he has found new\nuses for old techniques,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 155330.0,
      "end_time": 158490.0,
      "text": "hiring craftspeople adept in\nancient joinery traditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 158490.0,
      "end_time": 161420.0,
      "text": "He has enlisted the most skilled\nporcelain makers in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 161420.0,
      "end_time": 164390.0,
      "text": "to demonstrate their mastery,\ncommissioning exquisitely made"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 164390.0,
      "end_time": 167180.0,
      "text": "copies and objects like\nwatermelons, crabs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 167180.0,
      "end_time": 170030.0,
      "text": "and millions and millions\nof sunflower seeds."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 170030.0,
      "end_time": 172520.0,
      "text": "He has embraced the handmade\nwithin an economy whose"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 172520.0,
      "end_time": 175670.0,
      "text": "incredible growth has been\nfueled by automation and mass"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 175670.0,
      "end_time": 176270.0,
      "text": "production."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 176270.0,
      "end_time": 179240.0,
      "text": "He has synthesized\ntraditionally Chinese materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 179240.0,
      "end_time": 181190.0,
      "text": "to think about the\npart in relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 181190.0,
      "end_time": 184430.0,
      "text": "to the whole, the self in\nrelationship to the collective."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 184430.0,
      "end_time": 187220.0,
      "text": "\"If a nation cannot face\nits past,\" he has said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 187220.0,
      "end_time": 188540.0,
      "text": "\"it has no future.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 188540.0,
      "end_time": 190820.0,
      "text": "And Ai is equally\nconcerned with the present."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 190820.0,
      "end_time": 193130.0,
      "text": "In 2008, when the Sichuan\nearthquake struck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 193130.0,
      "end_time": 195470.0,
      "text": "he visited the region in\nthe immediate aftermath"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 195470.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "and assembled volunteers to\ngather the names of the dead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200450.0,
      "text": "addressing attempts by\nauthorities to cover up"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 200450.0,
      "end_time": 203390.0,
      "text": "the disproportionate number of\nschoolchildren who died because"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 203390.0,
      "end_time": 204830.0,
      "text": "of poorly built schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 204830.0,
      "end_time": 207770.0,
      "text": "He amassed tons of twisted\nrebar from the wreckage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 207770.0,
      "end_time": 210200.0,
      "text": "painstakingly straightened\nit, and assembled it"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 210200.0,
      "end_time": 212540.0,
      "text": "into spare elegiac memorials."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 212540.0,
      "end_time": 215730.0,
      "text": "He arranged 9,000 backpacks\non the facade of the Haus der"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 215730.0,
      "end_time": 219200.0,
      "text": "Kunst to Munich to represent\nthe young lives lost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 219200.0,
      "end_time": 221510.0,
      "text": "spelling out a quote\nfrom a victim's mother."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 221510.0,
      "end_time": 225010.0,
      "text": "\"She lived happily for\nseven years in this world.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 225010.0,
      "end_time": 227240.0,
      "text": "Ai has been a ceaseless,\nunflagging voice"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 227240.0,
      "end_time": 228410.0,
      "text": "for the voiceless."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 228410.0,
      "end_time": 231590.0,
      "text": "In 2009, he was beaten and\ndetained in his hotel room"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 231590.0,
      "end_time": 233990.0,
      "text": "in Chengdu when\nattempting to testify"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 233990.0,
      "end_time": 236780.0,
      "text": "in the trial of human\nrights activist Tan Zuoren."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 236780.0,
      "end_time": 239510.0,
      "text": "He visits with refugees\nfleeing the war in Syria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 239510.0,
      "end_time": 242150.0,
      "text": "organized a London walk of\ncompassion in their honor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 242150.0,
      "end_time": 244370.0,
      "text": "covered his sculptures\nwith thermal blankets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 244370.0,
      "end_time": 246680.0,
      "text": "and wrapped the columns\nof Berlin's concert hall"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 246680.0,
      "end_time": 248660.0,
      "text": "with salvaged\nrefugee life vests."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 248660.0,
      "end_time": 250760.0,
      "text": "An early adherent\nof social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 250760.0,
      "end_time": 253010.0,
      "text": "he's an adamant\nsupporter of free speech."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 253010.0,
      "end_time": 255470.0,
      "text": "He reports on his\nlife in minute detail."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 255470.0,
      "end_time": 258800.0,
      "text": "He did so up until his\n2011 arrest and confinement"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 258800.0,
      "end_time": 261860.0,
      "text": "for 81 days on unfounded\ntax evasion charges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 261860.0,
      "end_time": 263000.0,
      "text": "as well as after."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 263000.0,
      "end_time": 265490.0,
      "text": "Authorities have demolished\nhis Shanghai studio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 265490.0,
      "end_time": 267890.0,
      "text": "threatened to demolish\nhis Beijing studio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 267890.0,
      "end_time": 269690.0,
      "text": "and forced him to\npay a tax evasion"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 269690.0,
      "end_time": 271610.0,
      "text": "fine of 15 million yuan."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 271610.0,
      "end_time": 273950.0,
      "text": "He has been continually\nsurveilled and followed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 273950.0,
      "end_time": 276530.0,
      "text": "prevented from leaving his\ncountry, and through it all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 276530.0,
      "end_time": 280160.0,
      "text": "has refused censorship within\nChina, as well as abroad."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 280160.0,
      "end_time": 282380.0,
      "text": "Not everything he\ndoes is genius."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 282380.0,
      "end_time": 285440.0,
      "text": "But he remains committed to\nreaching an ever wider public."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 285440.0,
      "end_time": 288110.0,
      "text": "His work does not sit\nfirmly in the realm of art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 288110.0,
      "end_time": 289270.0,
      "text": "but radiates out."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 289270.0,
      "end_time": 291230.0,
      "text": "He's often called an iconoclast."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 291230.0,
      "end_time": 292790.0,
      "text": "And an urn crusher\nwould certainly"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 292790.0,
      "end_time": 294660.0,
      "text": "seem to adhere to\nthe definition."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 294660.0,
      "end_time": 297020.0,
      "text": "But there's another way to\nsee Ai Weiwei, as someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 297020.0,
      "end_time": 299150.0,
      "text": "who desperately wants\nthe cherished beliefs"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 299150.0,
      "end_time": 302060.0,
      "text": "and institutions of China's\npast to be remembered"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 302060.0,
      "end_time": 303110.0,
      "text": "and resuscitated."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 303110.0,
      "end_time": 305090.0,
      "text": "And in that sense,\nas radicals go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 305090.0,
      "end_time": 306770.0,
      "text": "he's brilliantly conservative."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 306770.0,
      "end_time": 309650.0,
      "text": "His work is deeply rooted\nin history and tradition."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 309650.0,
      "end_time": 312950.0,
      "text": "It is steeped in remembering,\nvaluing, preserving."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 312950.0,
      "end_time": 315170.0,
      "text": "He stands defiantly\nopposed to a culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 315170.0,
      "end_time": 317810.0,
      "text": "that wants to move on with\nlittle regard for the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 317810.0,
      "end_time": 320600.0,
      "text": "He has resistance to\nforgetting, to silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 320600.0,
      "end_time": 324230.0,
      "text": "His work asks us to consider\nwhat we value, why we value it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 324230.0,
      "end_time": 327050.0,
      "text": "and what we are accountable\nfor destroying, preserving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 327050.0,
      "end_time": 328070.0,
      "text": "or transforming."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 328070.0,
      "end_time": 330830.0,
      "text": "He asks fundamental questions\nabout our human rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 330830.0,
      "end_time": 332120.0,
      "text": "and responsibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 332120.0,
      "end_time": 335540.0,
      "text": "Liberty,\" he says, 'is about our\nrights to question everything.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 335540.0,
      "end_time": 337700.0,
      "text": "Out of a source of\nconstant irritation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 337700.0,
      "end_time": 339370.0,
      "text": "the oyster develops a pearl."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 339370.0,
      "end_time": 341780.0,
      "text": "Ai is that constant\nsource of irritation."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 341780.0,
      "end_time": 344520.0,
      "text": "And we are lucky not only\nto bear witness to it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 344520.0,
      "end_time": 346460.0,
      "text": "but to be called\nto action by it."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 346460.0,
      "end_time": 349210.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    }
  ]
}